  <brief_title>Oral Bioavailability of GLPG0555 in Different Solid Formulations</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open Label, 3-way Crossover Study to Compare the Oral Bioavailability of GLPG0555 After Single-dose Intake in Healthy Subjects as a Solid Dispersion Formulation, With and Without Food, Relative to a Nanosuspension Formulation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
