  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to compare the pharmacokinetics of a solid capsule formulation of
      GLPG0555 with a nanosuspension, and to assess safety and tolerability of a single dose of
      GLPG0555.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
